<p>Hey there, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/saugori" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6901921); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6901921&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602084539" alt="Saugori" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6901921)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/saugori" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6901921); return false;">Saugori</a></span>. Welcome to the SCP Wiki!</p>
<p>Glad to see you're interested in reading around the site and decided to join the community. Seeing that you're here to read around, I suggest you check out some of the newer top-rated articles. Personally, I recommend reading <a href="/scp-5140">SCP-5140</a>. It's fantastically eerie and alludes to a lot. Anyway, here's some stuff that'll help you out around the site:</p>
<h3><span>Navigation:</span></h3>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
