<p>A tad belated, but hello SinfulSorrow!</p>
<p>Welcome to the wiki! Joining the site to get inspired by reading more content is a great place to start. I've left you with my reading list to hopefully make your journey through the wiki a bit easier! I can agree that the forums can be a bit overwhelming haha, but usually you can figure things about by looking around + feel free to ask questions if you have any.</p>
<p>As for your question about S-CSS-P, as far as I'm aware there is not, but I may be wrong about this. Regardless though, I hope you enjoy your time here, and best of luck with your skip whenever you do write it!</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+Here&nbsp;are&nbsp;some&nbsp;places&nbsp;to&nbsp;start.</a></div>
